<subSubSection id="C328ABCEFFB448057BB0FC8DFEDC4B3A" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8B8DF845FFB448057BB0FC8DFE954C6F" blockId="9.[189,310,861,887]" box="[189,310,861,887]" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">Diagnosis</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8DF845FFB448057BB0FC4EFEDC4B3A" blockId="9.[188,1398,926,1058]" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">
Species with incomplete notauli and smooth mesoscutum like 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB4480578ABFC4FFB9D4CA0" authorityName="Fergusson" authorityYear="1985" box="[934,1086,927,953]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atricornis">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB4480578ABFC4FFB9D4CA0" box="[934,1086,927,953]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. atricornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB448057F40FC4FFB514CA0" authorityName="♀ V. Belizin" authorityYear="1951" box="[1101,1266,926,953]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longicellus">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB448057F40FC4FFB514CA0" box="[1101,1266,926,953]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. longicellus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB448057E0CFC4FFAD54CA0" authorityName="Belizin" authorityYear="1961" box="[1281,1398,927,953]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paucus">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB448057E0CFC4FFAD54CA0" box="[1281,1398,927,953]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. paucus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB448057BFCFC12FECC4CC3" authorityName="Kovalev" authorityYear="1974" box="[241,367,962,988]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zaitzevi">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB448057BFCFC12FECC4CC3" box="[241,367,962,988]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. zaitzevi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, from which can be distinguished by having alutaceous scutellum slightly projected at the end (scutellum areolate and not dorsally projected in 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB448057897FC35FB964CE6" authorityName="Fergusson" authorityYear="1985" box="[922,1077,997,1023]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atricornis">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB448057897FC35FB964CE6" box="[922,1077,997,1023]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. atricornis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB448057F48FC35FB4E4CE6" authorityName="♀ V. Belizin" authorityYear="1951" box="[1093,1261,996,1023]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longicellus">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB448057F48FC35FB4E4CE6" box="[1093,1261,996,1023]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. longicellus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB448057FF3FC35FAD54CE6" authorityName="Belizin" authorityYear="1961" box="[1278,1398,997,1023]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paucus">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB448057FF3FC35FAD54CE6" box="[1278,1398,997,1023]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. paucus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C3283C6FFB448057BFDFBD8FECE4B3A" authorityName="Kovalev" authorityYear="1974" box="[240,365,1032,1058]" class="Insecta" family="Figitidae" genus="Aegilips" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zaitzevi">
<emphasis id="B9462457FFB448057BFDFBD8FECE4B3A" box="[240,365,1032,1058]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="117">A. zaitzevi</emphasis>
